sets.tps: 200 HP, 60 En, 200 M Def, 40 R Def / 44 En, 56 R Def
sets.detail:
200 Health and 200 Melee Defense with Very Robust are to be as Melee bulky as possible 
 60 Energy = 253 Energy at level 50 for (2 Battering Rams + 3 Geysers) with Heavy Armor 
 44 Energy = 250 Energy at level 50 for (2 Battering Rams + 3 Geysers and 2 Braces) without Heavy Armor 
 40/56 Ranged Defense are leftovers and improve overall bulk
sets.author: Epicly Epic Gamer
